designJobs.brief:
Iron Clad Team Store — Creative & Product Brief
Overall Theme
A professional athletic look — the type of gear you’d see and want to buy in a premium sportswear store.
Inspired by brands like Ruka and Athletics.


Combines clean, performance-focused design with subtle military and American flag influences.


Select pieces feature modern camo variations (especially t-shirts).


High-end athletic aesthetic — sleek, durable, and unified across all items.



Branding & Design Details
Iron Clad logo: always placed high on the back — the signature look.


Color Direction: Red, Blue, Charcoal, Black, White, Olive, and subdued Camo tones.


Design Elements:


Minimal but bold.


Integrate flag themes tastefully (e.g., sleeve patch, side panel, or tonal print).


Use premium textures and materials for a true performance-wear feel.



Product Lineup
Performance Apparel
Singlets (2 total) — Red and Blue versions


Competition-approved for Freestyle and Greco


Option to add athlete’s last name on the back


Clean base with subtle flag or camo accenting


Hooded T-Shirt (Light Hoodie)


Poly-spandex blend


Short-sleeve with attached hood — lightweight training piece


Available in flag or camo variations


Quarter Zip Pullover


Performance fit for warm-ups


Small logo on front, high logo on back


Crew Neck Sweatshirt


Premium athletic fleece


Minimalist design with tonal or embroidered logo


Sweats (Joggers)


Athletic taper fit


Optional logo and flag patch


Shorts


Training shorts — poly blend with stretch


Match colorway of singlets and tops


Short-Sleeve & Long-Sleeve Shirts


Lightweight, athletic fit


Camo and American flag themed variations


Socks


Branded Iron Clad athletic socks


Optional flag detailing or logo wrap



Store Presentation
Unified product photography with consistent lighting and model poses.


Lifestyle images to showcase the “store-bought, professional athlete” look.


Consider labeling sections:


“Training Essentials”


“Competition Ready”


“American Grit Collection”
